Period. Wooden house box inscribed "PERIOD". Inside, color slides of Vincent Fecteau's artwork ranging in dates from 1994-1999. Color printer copy of a house. Color photographs of carnival including buildings, rides, backstage and props. Magazine photograph of a young man. Period diagram and letter, text scribbled out, still legible.
